This USB Connection Scanner includes:
- Real-time USB device monitoring
- Detailed device information (USB standard, speed, class, driver)
- Kernel device detection (/dev/sr0, /dev/sda, etc.)
- GUI and CLI modes
- Activity logging with timestamps

